Titolo: Operation Flashpoint: Red Hammer

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Operation Flashpoint: Red Hammer is an expansion pack to Operation Flashpoint: Cold War Crisis. It was developed by Codemasters.
Red Hammer depicts the same conflict as Operation Flashpoint: Cold War Crisis, but places the player in the role of a Soviet soldier, Dmitri Lukin, rather than a U.S. soldier.